From working/stay at home life and pumping to having multiple kids and busy lives, you’re all super parents. Here’s a day in the life.

⭐ Life with Nanobébé makes parenting a little bit more convenient
🎥 @malgalcinemas 
.

***Giveaway Closed*** Congrats to @ceejaylauretta on winning!!! 🍼PUMP IT UP GIVEAWAY🍼⁠
⁠
Get pumped! Whether you're power pumping, exclusively pumping, combination feeding, or just getting started in your pumping journey - here's the ultimate giveaway for you! One lucky mama will win all of these essentials (a $750 value!) perfect for their pumping journey.⁠
⁠
How to enter:⁠
⭐ Like this post⁠
⭐ Follow ALL 5 awesome brands tagged below⁠
⭐ Tell us about your pumping game in the comments (multitasking while hands-free pumping, supplementing, pregnant and planning to pump, etc)⁠
⁠
For an additional entry, head to the link in our bio!⁠
⁠
Winner will receive:⁠
⁠
🍼 @nanobebe_world Pumping Essentials like Breastmilk Bottles with Pump Adapter, Breastmilk Storage Bags and More, $200 value⁠
🍼 @medela_us Pump In Style with MaxFlow Double Electric Breast Pump Featuring Exclusive New Technology and a Modern Design, $250 value⁠
🍼 @boobiebar Milk-Boosting Lactation Products and Superfoods for Hydration, Milk Support and More, $100 value⁠
🍼 @the_dairyfairy Ruby All-In-One Nursing and Handsfree Pumping Bralettes (One in Black and One in Cream Color), $100 value⁠
🍼 @idaho_jones Chertsey Breast Pump Backpack & Roxwell Milk Cooler Insulated Bag, $110 value⁠
⁠
Entries are being accepted on both Instagram and Facebook, so head over to FB for an extra chance to win! Giveaway ends 8/25 at 11:59 pm PST. Must be 18 or older to enter. Open to US and CA residents. Giveaway not affiliated with Instagram. ⁠
DISCLAIMER: We do NOT create separate giveaway accounts for contacting winners, nor do we ever ask giveaway winners for payment information for any reason ever.
